{"tid":2235708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「內循環」十一長假 大陸旅遊業收入跌逾三成","createTime":"2020-10-09T02:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T03:35:03.000Z","uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c229529d8baafa69d866be1153114f742676bc","tid":2235708,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"中共病毒疫情爆發後迎來首個中國十一長假，民間消費復甦與否蔚為話題。連日來，中共官媒（<span class=\"red\">官方數字</span>）多次強調旅遊等消費顯著復甦。但中共文旅部發佈的旅遊消費復甦跟不上人潮復甦的數據，引發熱議。自由亞洲引述分析指出，今年「十一」旅遊人數與去年同期相比，降幅非常大，除中共病毒疫情之外，主要原因還是中國經濟每況愈下，導致居民的消費能力大幅下降。<br />\n<br />\n十一假期市道低迷  收入暴跌逾三成<br />\n中共文化和旅遊部數據中心的統計稱，10月1日至4日，全國國內遊客共4.25億人次，旅遊收入3,120.2億元，與去年同期相比分別「同比恢復」人數約78%、旅遊收入約68%。換句話說，今年長假的前4天，國內遊客人數比去年同期下跌了22%，旅遊收入下降了32%。這還是經過「灌水」的數據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-10-09/53072355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-10-09%2F53072355&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrznF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=ce7727f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-10-09/53072355</a>"},{"pid":"f71d0fffcbc6c870dab2aa65e51d2e2926d98ff5","tid":2235708,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:07:02.000Z","msg":"留名睇維尼食屎圖"},{"pid":"71d709d4a6c01b1f84b1ca16c12587a9fbb89ba8","tid":2235708,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:07:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"512a5a89fe85213e84fc7c8a3d1e236635d2e649","tid":2235708,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><spa